{"tid":1810650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"旅發局支持獨立調查","createTime":"2020-01-04T05:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T05:52:38.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3b914ad72ce20f60ff2f9071a0b34194cfd02169","tid":1810650,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】旅發局除夕抽獎接連出現問題，總幹事程鼎一指，已要求承辦商提交詳細報告，亦邀請第三方公司作獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局除夕抽獎接連有問題，總幹事程鼎一表示，曾為抽獎程式做壓力測試，可容納每分鐘三百萬人次，但到接受報名當日程式出現問題，加上要短時間內收發大量電郵，令電郵供應商誤認為垃圾郵件，承認因時間倉卒而準備不足。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，旅發局已要求承辦商提交詳細報告，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">邀請第三方公司作獨立調查</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375516&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDgAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=60f2a63f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375516&h=ebba972a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375516</a><br />\n<br />\n好不安。旅發局網站明明係亞洲最佳，點解要獨立調查？<br />\n獨立調查會影響旅發局員工士氣<br />\n咁多人同時登入旅發局網站，明顯係濫用，係黑客攻擊，應該報警捉參加抽獎的市民，罪名係&ldquo;不誠實取用電腦&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/miJvzJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmiJvzJA.jpg&h=64dc0286&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ac081965455fdb9f22d02faaf89ffee033ff44a","tid":1810650,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:49:24.000Z","msg":"N重標準<br />\n<br />\n龍門任你搬"},{"pid":"30c63b9ba9e2eed61eb44b085342b3b9b46c9f15","tid":1810650,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"市民濫用登記抽獎服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}